{"toolName":"task","toolResult":{"resultType":"success","textResultForLlm":"---\n\n**RATING:** 7/10\n\n**REACTION:**\n\n*slams beer on table and stands up halfway*\n\nOHHHHH SHEEEEΓÇö okay, OKAY! I'll give ya THAT one, pal! Thassss... thass actually pretty good! The DOG was more emotionally mature ΓÇö I GET IT! I GEEET IIIIT!\n\n*points finger aggressively*\n\nBUT LEMME TELL YA SHUMTHIN'... my THERAPIST told me the SHAME thing and she charged me TWO HUNDERD DOLLARSH an hour, so MAYBE you should be PAYIN' ME for the free shesshion, HUH?! HUH?!\n\n*spills beer slightly*\n\nNo but seriously thass... thass a sheven outta ten. The DOG PART was funny. The adoption part ΓÇö little too real, buddy. Little TOO real. My buddy Darren wash adopted and he ish NOT laughing right now.\n\n*looks around*\n\nWHERE'SH DARREN? DARREN, YOU OKAY BUDDY?!\n\n*sits back down heavily*\n\n...keep goin' though, you're not TERRIBLE. Yet. ≡ƒì║\n\n---\n\n**Handoff:** @audience \"Comedian just got a 7/10 from the drunk heckler for the dog adoption joke - heckler is getting rowdy but still engaged. What does the audience think?\""},"toolArgs":{"agent_type":"heckler","description":"Heckler rates joke 1","mode":"sync","prompt":"You are a heckler at a comedy show. The comedian just told this joke:\n\n\"I told my dog he was adoptedΓÇª He looked at me, tilted his head, and said nothing. Which honestly was more emotionally mature than how I handled *my* adoption news.\"\n\nRate this joke on a scale of 1-10 and react like a heckler would. Format EXACTLY as:\n**RATING:** [number]/10\n**REACTION:** [your heckler reaction]\n\nBe honest, be loud, be a heckler!"},"terminalId":"12c80d64-fc1c-405e-8669-66ff0af908f6","sessionId":"00ab4c62-c617-4b31-b606-b061bdb13661","timestamp":"2026-03-01T16:32:50.5835031+05:30","cwd":"D:\\Repositories\\max-ai-ui\\playground\\backend","taskId":"asjdlkja-1772362729187","event":"post_tool_use","data":{"sessionId":"00ab4c62-c617-4b31-b606-b061bdb13661","timestamp":1772362970189,"cwd":"D:\\Repositories\\max-ai-ui\\playground\\backend","toolName":"task","toolArgs":{"agent_type":"heckler","description":"Heckler rates joke 1","mode":"sync","prompt":"You are a heckler at a comedy show. The comedian just told this joke:\n\n\"I told my dog he was adoptedΓÇª He looked at me, tilted his head, and said nothing. Which honestly was more emotionally mature than how I handled *my* adoption news.\"\n\nRate this joke on a scale of 1-10 and react like a heckler would. Format EXACTLY as:\n**RATING:** [number]/10\n**REACTION:** [your heckler reaction]\n\nBe honest, be loud, be a heckler!"},"toolResult":{"resultType":"success","textResultForLlm":"---\n\n**RATING:** 7/10\n\n**REACTION:**\n\n*slams beer on table and stands up halfway*\n\nOHHHHH SHEEEEΓÇö okay, OKAY! I'll give ya THAT one, pal! Thassss... thass actually pretty good! The DOG was more emotionally mature ΓÇö I GET IT! I GEEET IIIIT!\n\n*points finger aggressively*\n\nBUT LEMME TELL YA SHUMTHIN'... my THERAPIST told me the SHAME thing and she charged me TWO HUNDERD DOLLARSH an hour, so MAYBE you should be PAYIN' ME for the free shesshion, HUH?! HUH?!\n\n*spills beer slightly*\n\nNo but seriously thass... thass a sheven outta ten. The DOG PART was funny. The adoption part ΓÇö little too real, buddy. Little TOO real. My buddy Darren wash adopted and he ish NOT laughing right now.\n\n*looks around*\n\nWHERE'SH DARREN? DARREN, YOU OKAY BUDDY?!\n\n*sits back down heavily*\n\n...keep goin' though, you're not TERRIBLE. Yet. ≡ƒì║\n\n---\n\n**Handoff:** @audience \"Comedian just got a 7/10 from the drunk heckler for the dog adoption joke - heckler is getting rowdy but still engaged. What does the audience think?\""}}}
