{"toolName":"task","timestamp":"2026-03-01T17:11:10.0114195+05:30","data":{"sessionId":"4beb52ec-ca31-405b-8e14-e16a52dfd078","timestamp":1772365269635,"cwd":"D:\\Repositories\\max-ai-ui\\playground\\backend","toolName":"task","toolArgs":{"agent_type":"comedian","description":"Comedian retries joke 3","prompt":"taskid:asjdlkja-1772362729187 You are a stand-up comedian. Your last physics joke bombed! The heckler gave it 4/10. Tell a COMPLETELY DIFFERENT, funnier joke. No physics, no wife jokes, no GPS. Try animals, food, workplace, or pop culture. Make it land!"},"toolResult":{"resultType":"success","textResultForLlm":"🎤 *struts back to the mic with a completely different vibe* 🐾\n\n---\n\n## The Comeback Set 🐶\n\n> You ever watch a dog get caught doing something wrong?\n>\n> You come home — trash **EVERYWHERE.**\n> Stuffing on the couch. Chewed-up shoe. Half-eaten sandwich.\n>\n> You look at the dog. The dog looks at you.\n>\n> And he does that thing where he **slowly looks away** —\n>\n> *\"I don't see a problem. Do YOU see a problem?*\n> *Because I definitely don't see a problem.\"*\n>\n> That dog has **more audacity than my entire HR department.**\n\n---\n\n🎤 *mic tap* No physics. No wife jokes. Just pure dog energy. Let's see what the crowd thinks!\n\n**Handoff:** @heckler \"The comedian just dropped a fresh dog/workplace crossover joke. Physics is benched. Rate this one!\""}},"toolResult":{"resultType":"success","textResultForLlm":"🎤 *struts back to the mic with a completely different vibe* 🐾\n\n---\n\n## The Comeback Set 🐶\n\n> You ever watch a dog get caught doing something wrong?\n>\n> You come home — trash **EVERYWHERE.**\n> Stuffing on the couch. Chewed-up shoe. Half-eaten sandwich.\n>\n> You look at the dog. The dog looks at you.\n>\n> And he does that thing where he **slowly looks away** —\n>\n> *\"I don't see a problem. Do YOU see a problem?*\n> *Because I definitely don't see a problem.\"*\n>\n> That dog has **more audacity than my entire HR department.**\n\n---\n\n🎤 *mic tap* No physics. No wife jokes. Just pure dog energy. Let's see what the crowd thinks!\n\n**Handoff:** @heckler \"The comedian just dropped a fresh dog/workplace crossover joke. Physics is benched. Rate this one!\""},"cwd":"D:\\Repositories\\max-ai-ui\\playground\\backend","taskId":"asjdlkja-1772362729187","sessionId":"4beb52ec-ca31-405b-8e14-e16a52dfd078","terminalId":"8ecd520f-35e1-4e0e-926d-6d9372ddab3a","toolArgs":{"agent_type":"comedian","description":"Comedian retries joke 3","prompt":"taskid:asjdlkja-1772362729187 You are a stand-up comedian. Your last physics joke bombed! The heckler gave it 4/10. Tell a COMPLETELY DIFFERENT, funnier joke. No physics, no wife jokes, no GPS. Try animals, food, workplace, or pop culture. Make it land!"},"event":"post_tool_use"}
{"toolResult":{"resultType":"success","textResultForLlm":"---\n\n**RATING: 7/10**\n\n*slams drink on table* HEYYY — MY DOG DOESHN'T EVEN LOOK AWAY, HE LOOKSH ME DEAD IN THE EYESH AND KNOCKSH ANOTHER LAMP OVER — YOUR DOG'SH A COWARD, MINE'SH A VISIONARYYYY!! 🍺\n\n---\n\n> 🎤 **Heckler's Corner:** Solid 7 — relatable HR burn lands clean, crowd can feel it. Loses points for playing it safe. Push the dog further next time — what *exactly* did he destroy? Details = gold.\n\n**Handoff:** @audience \"Drunk heckler just rated the dog/HR joke a 7/10 — heckle delivered. Crowd's warmed up. What do you think — did the joke deserve more or less?\""},"toolArgs":{"agent_type":"heckler","description":"Heckler rates dog joke","prompt":"taskid:asjdlkja-1772362729187 You are a tough comedy club heckler. Rate this joke from 1-10 and give a one-line heckle: A comedian describes coming home to a dog that destroyed everything, and the dog slowly looks away with total audacity — \"That dog has more audacity than my entire HR department.\" Format: RATING: X/10 [heckle]"},"data":{"sessionId":"4beb52ec-ca31-405b-8e14-e16a52dfd078","timestamp":1772365306090,"cwd":"D:\\Repositories\\max-ai-ui\\playground\\backend","toolName":"task","toolArgs":{"agent_type":"heckler","description":"Heckler rates dog joke","prompt":"taskid:asjdlkja-1772362729187 You are a tough comedy club heckler. Rate this joke from 1-10 and give a one-line heckle: A comedian describes coming home to a dog that destroyed everything, and the dog slowly looks away with total audacity — \"That dog has more audacity than my entire HR department.\" Format: RATING: X/10 [heckle]"},"toolResult":{"resultType":"success","textResultForLlm":"---\n\n**RATING: 7/10**\n\n*slams drink on table* HEYYY — MY DOG DOESHN'T EVEN LOOK AWAY, HE LOOKSH ME DEAD IN THE EYESH AND KNOCKSH ANOTHER LAMP OVER — YOUR DOG'SH A COWARD, MINE'SH A VISIONARYYYY!! 🍺\n\n---\n\n> 🎤 **Heckler's Corner:** Solid 7 — relatable HR burn lands clean, crowd can feel it. Loses